videos.headline: Davion Warren hauls in the rock and throws down the hammer for Texas Tech
videos.description: Marcus Santos-Silva somehow saves the rock and dishes it to Davion Warren for the massive jam to extend the Red Raiders' lead in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Marcus Santos-Silva makes a great defensive play for the steal) 2022/02/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Adonis Arms finds a wide-open Bryson Williams for a Texas Tech flush
videos.description: Bryson Williams hauls in the laser from Adonis Arms and unleashes a massive jam for the Red Raiders.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bryson Williams rocks the rim with powerful dunk) 2022/02/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mike Miles lets it fly and drills the 3 from deep for TCU
videos.description: Mike Miles buries the 3-pointer despite tight coverage to tie the game at 7-7.

videos.headline: Terrence Shannon somehow gets the and-1 to fall for Texas Tech
videos.description: Terrence Shannon Jr. muscles through three TCU defenders somehow knocks down the and-1 to pull the Horned Frogs within two.

videos.headline: Adonis Arms jumps out of the gym for this Texas Tech jam
videos.description: Adonis Arms activates his jet pack and flies to the rim for the massive flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (This dunk from Adonis Arms was too nice) 2022/02/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mike Miles has spings in his kicks and he launches for a TCU slam
videos.description: Mike Miles soars through the paint and throws it down to pull the Horned Frogs within eight.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mike Miles throws down powerful jam vs. Texas Tech Red Raiders) 2022/02/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chuck O'Bannon gets it done on both sides of the ball for TCU
videos.description: Chuck O'Bannon Jr. steals the rock and finishes with the smooth layup for the Horned Frogs. (edited)

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Chuck O'Bannon Jr. makes a great defensive play for the steal) 2022/02/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davion Warren gets it done on both ends of the court for Texas Tech
videos.description: Davion Warren gets the steal and hustles to the rim for the big-time flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Davion Warren elevates for slam vs. TCU Horned Frogs) 2022/02/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Xavier Cork rocks the rim to seal the victory for TCU
videos.description: Xavier Cork gathers the rock and throws down the hammer to seal the upset victory over No. 9 Texas Tech at home.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Xavier Cork rocks the rim with flush) 2022/02/26 ESHEET
